__package__.yml.rawContents:
service:
  auth: false
  base-path: ''
  endpoints:
    createUser:
      path: /user
      method: POST
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      request:
        name: UserCreate
        body:
          properties:
            username: string
            password: string
            confirmPassword: optional<string>
            email: string
        content-type: application/json
      response:
        docs: Success
        type: User
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - request:
            username: username
            password: password
            email: email
          response:
            body:
              id: id
              createdAt: '2024-01-15T09:30:00Z'
              updatedAt: '2024-01-15T09:30:00Z'
              name: name
              email: email
    createAccount:
      path: /account
      method: POST
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      request:
        body: Account
        content-type: application/json
      response:
        docs: Success
        type: Account
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - request:
            name: name
          response:
            body:
              id: id
              accountNumber: accountNumber
              balance: 1.1
              pin: pin
              securityQuestion: securityQuestion
              name: name
              email: email
  source:
    openapi: ../openapi.yml
types:
  User:
    properties:
      id:
        type: optional<string>
        access: read-only
      createdAt:
        type: optional<datetime>
        access: read-only
      updatedAt:
        type: optional<datetime>
        access: read-only
      name: string
      email: string
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  Account:
    properties:
      id:
        type: optional<string>
        access: read-only
      accountNumber:
        type: optional<string>
        access: read-only
      balance:
        type: optional<double>
        access: read-only
      pin:
        type: optional<string>
        access: write-only
      securityQuestion:
        type: optional<string>
        access: write-only
      name: string
      email: optional<string>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml

rootApiFile.rawContents:
name: api
error-discrimination:
  strategy: status-code
display-name: ReadOnly/WriteOnly Edge Cases
